# We exclude kids who are outside of the 6-9 or 12-15 month age range. 
d <- d %>%
  mutate(out_of_age = case_when(
    age_mo < 6 ~ TRUE,
    age_mo > 15 ~ TRUE,
    age_mo > 9 & age_mo < 12 ~ TRUE,
    TRUE ~ FALSE
  ))
